headline: Why Fair Isaac Corporation (FICO) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of credit scoring and analytics company FICO (NYSE:FICO) jumped 3.8% in the morning session after Raymond James raised its price target on the company's stock to $1,940 from $1,800.
